messages.message: One of the issues we have is that these tables can have any series of headers, can be an image, word doc or an excel. Also they tend to span multiple pages. Unfortunately this is the only fake example we have, all the other examples have real data so we can't bring it outside their env.
Bringing in @Vishnu who has been leading this use case at AXA UK for more context if you have any further questions.
We are working on multi-page table support
Any idea on if this is likely to make the 23.07 release? We are making a big push client side for approval, so want to be cautious as to what use cases we use as the business driver
